{
  "text": "There were three types of biochemical analysis. These are Free Fatty Acid (FFA), Peroxide Value (POV) and Thiobarbituric Acid value (TBARS). FFA value was determined according to [CITATION_1] . POV was determined according to [CITATION_2] . Lipid oxidation was assessed in triplicate using the 2-thiobarbituric acid (TBA) method described by [CITATION_3] .",
  "correct_citation": {
    "[CITATION_1]": "33242242",
